    "description": {
      "value": "<p>On your turn, you can use a bonus action and expend one superiority die to bolster the resolve of one of your companions. When you do so, choose a friendly creature who can see or hear you. That creature gains temporary hit points equal to the superiority die roll + your Charisma modifier.</p>\n<p>Beginning at 7th fighter level, the number of temporary hit points the creature gains is equal to the superiority die roll + your Proficiency bonus + your Charisma modifier.</p>",
